Package: data.ca.gov
Title: California Open Data (CKAN) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the California Open Data CKAN API. Covers
